21
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:35,880
=Episode 21=

22
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,039
Lu Jing.

23
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,280
Sudah datang.

24
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:43,120
Kenapa cepat sekali?

25
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:46,759
Setelah tahu kau mau datang,
aku segera kemari.

26
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:50,479
Di sini masih ada orang.

27
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,759
Ada apa dengan kalian?

28
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:55,320
Yutou.

29
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:57,120
Kau sudah selesai masak?

30
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:58,880
Liang Chen lapar seharian.

31
00:01:59,280 --> 00:01:59,880
Cepat pergi.

32
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,200
Cepat masak.

33
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:03,720
Ini rumahku, aku bukan koki.

34
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:14,800
Tadi bicara apa?

35
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,160
Dua hari lagi ulang tahun
Kak Jiayun,…

36
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,040
…aku dan Yutou diskusi
mau menghadiahkan apa.

37
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,040
Kapan dia ulang tahun?

38
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,560
Tanggal 24 bulan ini.

39
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,680
Malam natal?

40
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:33,560
Hari ulang tahunnya
dipilih dengan sangat bagus.

41
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:36,880
Aku bahkan lupa malam natal.

42
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:40,600
Ini adalah festival pertama
sejak kita bersama.

43
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:42,720
Namun, tak baik jika aku tak
ke tempat Kak Jiayun.

44
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,960
Aku sudah janji padanya.

45
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:47,400
Tak masalah, aku bantu kau
pilih hadiah.

46
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,079
Kau tak marah?

47
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,600
Memberi hadiah itu wajar.

48
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,560
Ayo.

49
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,960
Lihat ini.

50
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,480
Bagaimana kalau beri ini?

51
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,320
Ini tak cocok.

52
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,080
Lihat lagi.

53
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,120
Dasi?

54
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,240
Dia pasti sudah punya banyak dasi.

55
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:09,160
Kancing manset?

56
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,560
Tak bagus.

57
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,640
Jadi, mau hadiahkan apa?

58
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,040
Ini saja.

59
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,940
Kura-kura kecil,
mempunyai makna bagus.

60
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,920
Sehat dan panjang umur.

61
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:23,240
Kau sengaja, 'kan?

62
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:27,320
Ini bagus, menggemaskan.

63
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:27,920
Kecuali…

64
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,079
Yang ini?

65
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,720
Ini lumayan.

66
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:36,640
Kalian sedang apa?

67
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:38,760
Ada apa ini?

68
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:44,040
Ini masih tak paham?

69
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,280
Beri aku petunjuk.

70
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,079
Ini cukup jelas, 'kan?

71
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,040
Ya ampun.

72
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,440
Apa aku mataku kabur?

73
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,280
Kalian bergandengan tangan?

74
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:01,660
Kau tak salah lihat,
memang seperti yang kau kira.

75
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,640
Apa tak ada yang mau
kau tanyakan pada kami?

76
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,960
Tanya apa?

77
00:04:11,580 --> 00:04:13,300
Kau boleh tanya seberapa
bahagianya kami.

78
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,440
Yutou.

79
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:21,000
Kalian bahagia saja berdua.

80
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:27,780
Sekarang bagaimana?

81
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,680
Kau mau nonton film?

82
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,720
Baik, sudah lama aku
tak nonton film.

83
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:35,080
Kebetulan di mobilku ada topi.

84
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,320
Ayo pergi nonton.

85
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,159
Berikan padaku!

86
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,000
Tidak.

87
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:43,680
Berikan!

88
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,920
Tidak.

89
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:03,480
Banyak orang, aku agak gugup.

90
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:07,760
Menggemaskan.

91
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:10,920
Apa?

92
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,040
Tak ada.

93
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:14,120
Film sudah diputar, fokuslah.

94
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,920
Bagaimana kalau aku
menari untukmu?

95
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,400
Kau suka?

96
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,440
Suka.

97
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,880
Jangan menangis lagi, ya?

98
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,440
Jangan menangis lagi.

99
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:36,880
Sangat lucukah?

100
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:42,080
Liu Maoyan sungguh menggemaskan.

101
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,240
Aku juga sama.

102
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:50,200
Siapa yang memujimu?

103
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:53,760
Bukankah kau bilang aku
mirip Liu Maoyan?

104
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:56,480
Kau memuji dia
berarti memujiku, 'kan?

105
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:02,760
Aku tak memujimu.

106
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,240
Halo.

107
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,080
Shanshan.

108
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:46,440
Apa kau bisa bilang
pada Liang Chen,…

109
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,360
…agar dia memilih musikku?

110
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,160
Nona Ma.

111
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:50,640
Kenapa dengan Liang Chen?

112
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:55,400
Nona Ma, lihat apa yang
kubawa untukmu?

113
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,680
Nona Ma, kelak jangan makan
makanan luar lagi.

114
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,560
Makanan luar tak baik
bagi tubuh.

115
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:19,400
Ayo, coba makan malam
yang kubuat.

116
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:22,320
Ini terlihat lebih enak dari
makanan luar.

117
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:26,560
Aku adalah pria baik yang bisa
bekerja keras dan bisa memasak.

118
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:29,040
Lihat betapa bagus warnanya.

119
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:30,640
Makanlah.

120
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:36,260
Kau bukannya mau bilang
tentang Liang Chen?

121
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,520
Dia kenapa?

122
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,600
Kau makan dulu.

123
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:41,240
Kuceritakan saat kau makan.

124
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:44,040
Cerita ini panjang.

125
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,360
Ceritakan dengan singkat.

126
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:52,520
Liang Chen sudah berpacaran.

127
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:55,600
Setiap hari mereka bermesraan.

128
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:58,760
Aku sudah tak tahan lagi.

129
00:10:58,920 --> 00:11:02,040
Bahkan aku tak bisa makan malam,
jadi, langsung datang mencarimu.

130
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:04,680
Apakah Kak Jiayun?

131
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:08,520
Kak Jiayun bukan
tipenya Liang Chen.

132
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,300
Nona Ma, kau sungguh
memahami Liang Chen.

133
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,520
Kalian memang teman sekelas.

134
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:25,800
Nona Ma, sebenarnya…

135
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,840
…aku sudah lama lajang.

136
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:37,880
Nona Ma.

137
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,120
Jujur saja.

138
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,880
Menurutmu, aku bagaimana?

139
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:45,240
Lumayan…

140
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,880
Kau juga merasa lumayan baik, 'kan?

141
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:49,200
Sebenarnya kau mau bilang apa?

142
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,080
Nona Ma, lihat.

143
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:54,080
Aku orang yang baik.

144
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:56,560
Aku juga bisa memasak,
karirku bagus.

145
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:59,480
Yang paling penting
adalah aku masih lajang.

146
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:02,280
Aku adalah pria yang berharga.

147
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,360
Nona Ma.

148
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:08,000
Apa kau tak punya perasaan khusus?

149
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:11,920
Sudah selesai bicara?

150
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,280
Pergilah kalau selesai.

151
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:21,000
Aku…

152
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:40,280
Silakan.

153
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:51,800
Kau makanlah lebih banyak.

154
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,440
Jika kau merasa masakanku…

155
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:08,680
Liu Maoyan cukup keren.

156
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:10,760
Ada satu kali kami bertemu
di suatu acara.

157
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:13,180
Dia bantu angkat gaunku
dan membantuku turun panggung.

158
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:16,080
Ternyata aktingnya bagus juga.

159
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,040
Menurutmu…

160
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,040
Kau tidak senang?

161
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,120
Filmnya tidak bagus?

162
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:33,320
Tak senang.

163
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,680
Kau memuji orang tampan.

164
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,480
Kau juga tampan.

165
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:44,080
Dia bantu kau angkat gaun
dan turun dari panggung.

166
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:50,680
Namun, aku bahkan
menggandeng tanganmu.

167
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:58,480
Kenapa? Sudah lebih senang?

168
00:13:58,800 --> 00:13:59,600
Sudah.

169
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:01,080
Namun, aku sedih.

170
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:03,680
Saat malam natal semuanya
rayakan bersama.

171
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,640
Hanya aku yang rayakan sendiri.

172
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,120
Sungguh kesepian.

173
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:12,200
Nanti saat acara ulang tahun,
aku pulang lebih awal.

174
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:13,960
Jangan memaksa.

175
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:16,480
Kau merayakan ulang tahun teman,
bagaimana bisa pulang cepat?

176
00:14:19,680 --> 00:14:20,280
Baiklah.

177
00:14:21,160 --> 00:14:21,880
Aku jemput kamu.

178
00:14:27,560 --> 00:14:28,800
Setelah selesai, kau kabari aku.

179
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:31,040
Jangan ubah jadwalmu demi aku.

180
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:34,360
Lagi pula, seberapa malam pun
aku bisa menunggumu.

181
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:39,520
Istirahatlah lebih awal,
selamat malam.

182
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:02,480
Kak Jiayun.

183
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:04,860
Selamat ulang tahun.

184
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:05,620
Terima kasih.

185
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:08,240
Ini hadiah untukmu.

186
00:15:08,280 --> 00:15:08,840
Kau suka?

187
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,200
Suka.

188
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:14,080
Kau cukup datang saja,
tak perlu bawa hadiah.

189
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:18,000
Yutou dan lainnya belum datang?

190
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:20,240
Duduklah dulu.

191
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:21,280
Baik.

192
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:42,440
Sudah lapar? Kita makan dulu.

193
00:15:43,160 --> 00:15:44,520
Yutou dan lainnya belum datang.

194
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:45,810
Tak baik
jika kita makan duluan.

195
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:49,040
Kita tunggu sambil makan.

196
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:52,520
Nona.

197
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:20,480
Kau mau pergi kencan?

198
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:23,400
Malam natal tentu harus
menemani pacar.

199
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:25,000
Yang benar saja.

200
00:16:25,520 --> 00:16:27,680
He Ye dan Liu Er sudah
pergi dari tadi.

201
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:31,000
Tak tahu kapan mereka
berdua mengejar perempuan.

202
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:33,240
Sekarang bahkan kau juga
mau keliaran di luar.

203
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:35,680
Inilah alasanmu tak dapat pacar.

204
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:37,240
Lu Jing.

205
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:39,320
Kau sungguh kejam.

206
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:41,200
Apa kau tahu demi
memberimu kejutan,…

207
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:43,400
…aku hampir berkelahi
dengan organisasi siswa.

208
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:44,440
Kejutan?

209
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,560
Kejutan apa?

210
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:48,880
Itu…

211
00:16:50,920 --> 00:16:52,520
Kau tunggu saja kejutanmu.

212
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:55,600
Sudahlah, pergilah temui pacarmu.

213
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:03,960
Tak tahu dari mana
pacarnya muncul.

214
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,560
Aku tak paham.

215
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:08,160
Kenapa mereka semua
punya pacar?

216
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:14,200
Apa aku tak tampan?

217
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:22,160
(Sun Binyu)

218
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:23,760
Kenapa?

219
00:17:24,109 --> 00:17:25,040
Bisa kenapa lagi?

220
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:27,240
Natal adalah acara penting.

221
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:30,640
Aku tentu harus mencari tahu
topik yang berguna darimu.

222
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:33,320
Contohnya, bagaimana kau
mengejar Liang Chen?

223
00:17:33,520 --> 00:17:36,800
Apa ada teknik khusus
yang bisa kau bagikan?

224
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:44,520
(Kirim)

225
00:17:44,520 --> 00:17:45,920
(Yutou)

226
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:47,560
(Kirim)

227
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,360
(Penjilat Bahagia, Lu Jing)
(Cara berbincang pria berbakat)

228
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,440
Lu Jing.

229
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:56,600
Bisakah kau lebih serius?

230
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:59,240
Aku sedang serius
bertanya padamu.

231
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:02,680
Kau masih bisa santai saat hadiri
pesta ulang tahun Ding Jiayun.

232
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:04,000
Aku tak pergi.

233
00:18:04,220 --> 00:18:06,380
Acara ulang tahun tiba-tiba
dibatalkan, kau tak tahu?

234
00:18:17,560 --> 00:18:19,720
Aku hampir selesai makan,
Yutou masih belum datang.

235
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:21,040
Tak disiplin waktu.

236
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,040
Kita makan kue saja.

237
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:26,360
Seharusnya malam ini,
mereka tak akan datang.

238
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:51,780
Silakan dinikmati.

239
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:03,280
Terima kasih.

240
00:19:09,080 --> 00:19:10,100
Aku bantu potong kue.

241
00:19:35,800 --> 00:19:37,560
Kenapa? Tak enak?

242
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,920
Tidak, karena…

243
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:44,640
Belakangan ini aku mau diet,
jadi, tak berani makan banyak.

244
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:48,240
Tak masalah, ini kupesan
dengan khusus,…

245
